<section class="site-section" id="building">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label">03 — Right Now</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">WHAT I'M BUILDING</h2>
    <div class="stair-cards">
      <div class="card tilt-card stair-card stair-1">
        <img src="/images/Limitless_Roofing_Solutions_-_4.png" alt="Limitless Roofing Solutions" class="card-logo" style="width:72px;height:72px;" />
        <div class="card-title" style="font-size:22px;">Limitless Roofing Solutions</div>
        <div class="card-body" style="font-size:16px;">Co-founding an AI-powered automation CRM with my partner Chase. Custom-built workflows for every roofing company's exact job flow, plus our Lead Secure System — when someone calls and nobody picks up, the caller instantly gets a custom text with links to schedule, fill out forms, leave reviews, or chat with an AI bot.</div>
        <span class="card-badge green">Active — Launching</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card tilt-card stair-card stair-2">
        <img src="/images/smallLucas_Project_Logo.png" alt="The Lucas Project" class="card-logo" style="width:60px;height:60px;" />
        <div class="card-title" style="font-size:20px;">The Lucas Project</div>
        <div class="card-body">Documenting the build in public across YouTube, Instagram, TikTok — the hub all roads lead back to.</div>
        <span class="card-badge teal">Always On</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card tilt-card stair-card stair-3">
        <img src="/images/ai-learning-communities-logo.png" alt="AI Learning Communities" class="card-logo" style="width:48px;height:auto;border-radius:4px;" />
        <div class="card-title" style="font-size:17px;">AI Learning Communities</div>
        <div class="card-body" style="font-size:14px;">Building a community and education platform to help real people learn and apply AI to their businesses and lives. Not theory — practical, applied, and built from the ground up alongside Limitless.</div>
        <span class="card-badge green">Active — Launching</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .stair-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr 0.8fr;
    gap: 24px;
    align-items: end;
  }
  .stair-1 { min-height: 440px; padding: 32px; }
  .stair-2 { min-height: 390px; padding: 28px; }
  .stair-3 { min-height: 310px; padding: 22px; }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .stair-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .stair-1, .stair-2, .stair-3 { min-height: auto; }
  }
</style>
